     1	# Configure HQ Authoritative Status
     2	
     3	This file is the human-facing source of truth for active development.
     4	Agents update it during planning, QA review, coding, and increment closeout so
     5	stakeholders can read one document instead of reconstructing state from chats,
     6	tests, or stash history.
     7	
     8	## Current Snapshot
     9	
